	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require burning incense and bits of earth and wood mixed with water.</p><p><br /><strong>Utility</strong></p><ul><li><p>You must be outdoors to cast this spell. If you move somewhere without a clear path to the sky, the spell ends early.</p></li><li><p>You take control of the weather in a 5-mile radius centered on you. The DM determines the starting weather based on climate and season.</p></li><li><p>You can alter precipitation, temperature, and wind. It takes [[/r 1d4*10]] minutes for changes to manifest.</p></li><li><p>Once the new conditions take effect, you may change them again. When the spell ends, the weather gradually reverts to normal.</p></li><li><p>When you change conditions, consult the following tables and move the current condition up or down by one stage. For wind, you may also choose its direction.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><table><caption>Precipitation</caption><thead><tr><th>Stage</th><th>Condition</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>Clear</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Light clouds</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>Overcast or ground fog</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>Rain, hail, or snow</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>Torrential rain, driving hail, or blizzard</td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption>Temperature</caption><thead><tr><th>Stage</th><th>Condition</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>Unbearable heat</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Hot</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>Warm</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>Cool</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>Cold</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>Arctic cold</td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption>Wind</caption><thead><tr><th>Stage</th><th>Condition</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>Calm</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Moderate wind</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>Strong wind</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>Gale</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>Storm</td></tr></tbody></table>",
			"chat": ""
		},
